definitions.definition: A heterocyclic amine found in both plant and animal tissue, where it is an intermediate in several metabolic schemes.
Any of a class of neurotransmitters and psychedelic drugs derived from this compound.

main_definition: ( uncountable , biochemistry ) A heterocyclic amine found in both plant and animal tissue, where it is an intermediate in several metabolic schemes.
